  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n    Specifically crafted HTML file and shared worker script can cause Use After Free of a TaskQueueImpl object in task  scheduling code TaskQueueImpl::CreateTaskRunner(). This bug may be exploited to achieve one click remote code execution in  renderer process."
